# Streamlit Custom Toggle

A custom component to load heart-shaped Toggle Switch widget

<p align="center">
 <a href="https://pypi.org/project/streamlit-custom-toggle/">
  <img src="https://badge.fury.io/py/streamlit-custom-toggle.svg" />
